<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<LibraryEntry xmlns="http://exocad.com/model/attachment">
	<Supplier>exocad GmbH</Supplier>
	<DisplayInformation>3D Print - Cutout for part removal from buildplate</DisplayInformation>
	<AttachmentPreviewFileName>preview.png</AttachmentPreviewFileName>
	<SupplierLogoFileName>logo.png</SupplierLogoFileName>
	<AttachmentDescription>
	
Cutout geometry for substraction from upper or lower jaw model, can be used for a better removal of 3D printed models from the 3D printer build plate and to avoid the vacuum effect with hollow models.

- Scalable in X/Y direction. 
- Free positioning along model height on outer curve.

</AttachmentDescription>	
	<Placement Move="XY" Rotate="Z">
		<Translation Axis="XY" Ref="_clickpoint"/>
		<Constraint Type="NoTranslationZ"/>
		<Constraint Type="OnPerimeter"/>
	</Placement>
	<ControlPoint Id="center" Type="ProjectPerimeter">
		<Alignment RelativeToBottom="true"/>
		<Location/>
	</ControlPoint>	
	<Parameter Id="Cutout" Scope="Single" Decimals="0" Min="4" Max="40" Default="8" Unit="mm">Depth of cutout</Parameter>
	<Parameter Id="WidthCutout" Scope="Single" Decimals="0" Min="2" Max="20" Default="8" Unit="mm">Width of cutout</Parameter>	
	<Component IfJaw="Any" Method="Subtractive" Id="anyaid">
		<Profile Mirror="true">
			<Point>
				<x>0</x>
				<z>2</z>
			</Point>
			<Point>
				<x>4</x>
				<z>2</z>
			</Point>
			<Point>
				<x>4</x>
				<z>0</z>
			</Point>
			<Point>
				<x>0</x>
				<z>0</z>
			</Point>			
			<Front Cap="Flat" Extrude="4"/>
			<Back Cap="Flat" Extrude="4"/>
		</Profile>
		<Scaling Axis="Y">
			<ParameterRef Coefficient="0.125">Cutout</ParameterRef>
			<Const>0.125</Const>
		</Scaling>
		<Scaling Axis="X">
			<ParameterRef Coefficient="0.125">WidthCutout</ParameterRef>
			<Const>0.125</Const>
		</Scaling>		
		<mat:Material xmlns:mat="http://exocad.com/config/color">
			<mat:Color>#453B6A</mat:Color>
			<mat:Opacity>0.5</mat:Opacity>
		</mat:Material>
		<Alignment Jaw="Any" RelativeToBottom="true"  AutoFlip="true"/>
		<Orientation Axis="Y" AroundAxis="Z" Ref="center" />
	</Component>
</LibraryEntry>